/* Quill Design System Theme
   Install: npx shadcn add https://quill-ds.vercel.app/r/quill.json
   Fonts: Fraunces (display/heading) + Raleway (body) from Google Fonts
*/

/* ─── Font imports ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
